1
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:34,680
Xuanqing ranked third in the exams.

2
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,920
We ought to celebrate.

3
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,160
But he won't hear of any fuss

4
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,920
and I dare not press the matter.

5
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,200
Still, appearances

6
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,280
must be kept.

7
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,960
I thought to

8
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,039
invite

9
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,080
Mrs. Yu

10
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,160
and Wanxue to dine with us.

11
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:52,920
What say you?

12
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,080
Mother's word is law.

13
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,680
No objections.

14
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,880
Those are your own words.

15
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,120
Then I shall

16
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,960
find you a match as well.

17
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,720
So Mother's been

18
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,120
setting a trap for me.

19
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,360
What nonsense.

20
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,759
I am nothing like you lot,

21
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,320
all cunning and hidden schemes.

22
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,920
Tell me true,

23
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,880
are you still

24
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:19,160
mourning

25
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,360
your late wife?

26
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,520
She was here

27
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:27,000
but two years.

28
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,560
You have mourned her

29
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,880
long enough.

30
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,600
To carry on

31
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,280
is too much!

32
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,440
It is not that.

33
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,400
I've simply been consumed by duties.

34
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,960
Yet even Xuanqing

35
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,640
is taking a bride now.

36
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,640
And you, his uncle,

37
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,400
remain utterly alone...

38
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,320
Then...

39
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,800
allow me to assist.

40
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,440
Whose daughter

41
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:56,240
has caught your favor?

42
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,440
Here we are again...

43
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,800
She needn't come

44
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,920
from a grand house.

45
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:04,920
So...

46
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:05,560
Forgive the intrusion.

47
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,760
There's a pressing matter with the Gus.

48
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,200
Mother,

49
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,880
I must

50
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,240
take my leave.

51
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,360
Every time marriage comes up,

52
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,240
something urgent appears.

53
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,040
Enjoy.

54
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,560
Off with you.

55
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,200
Since the Baoxiang Temple murders,

56
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,800
the bureau's been

57
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,800
watching this gang.

58
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,600
They made arrests just days ago.

59
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,040
And sent a list:

60
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,880
the gang itself,

61
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,040
plus everyone

62
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,120
linked to their dealings.

63
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,360
I went through it,

64
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,240
and there was

65
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,160
Ms. Gu's own brother.

66
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,520
I pressed a little further.

67
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,680
Word is, he operates

68
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,280
a gambling den.

69
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,160
A few from this gang

70
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,600
were his regulars.

71
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,640
A classic Ji, I must say.

72
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,280
No deal too dirty for that lot.

73
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,840
From what we've gathered,

74
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,079
Master Gu

75
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:55,880
certainly had no clue

76
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:56,880
who he was dealing with.

77
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,560
So when does the bureau

78
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,040
plan to wrap this up?

79
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:01,920
Lord Zhang

80
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,960
wants to move fast,

81
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,440
but wanted to check with you first.

82
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,080
Moving fast is the right call.

83
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,200
In that case,

84
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,240
go tip off Ms. Gu.

85
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,120
My lord.

86
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,000
On second thought...

87
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,600
tell her

88
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,519
I need to see her in person.

89
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,440
No matter what,

90
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,519
we have to meet.

91
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:24,400
Yes, my lord.

92
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,280
Go.

93
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,400
Ms. Gu,

94
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,520
this way.

95
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:36,880
Gratitude.

96
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,240
Stay put.

97
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:38,960
My lady.

98
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,240
Greetings, my lord.

99
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:55,720
No formalities.

100
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,680
This concerns your brother,

101
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,080
and it is no small matter.

102
00:04:59,280 --> 00:04:59,920
So

103
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,800
I wanted to meet you in person.

104
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,360
How can you be certain

105
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,720
he was unaware

106
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,760
of his clients' true nature?

107
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,080
I knew all along

108
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,720
he was a gambling tout.

109
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,760
But with our mother gravely ill,

110
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,240
I chose to say nothing.

111
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,280
Forgive me if it sounds foolish,

112
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,920
but he never...

113
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,920
cared much for studies.

114
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,280
He has a taste for trade.

115
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,000
Our family forbade it,

116
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,560
and so... he strayed.

117
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,960
But to say he conspired with outlaws...

118
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,320
he would never dare!

119
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,560
Can you vouch for that?

120
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,280
I'd stake my life on it.

121
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,400
As for

122
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,040
those outlaws,

123
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,000
the bureau's set to

124
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,400
make their move within days.

125
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,400
If you want to get him out,

126
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,960
you must act quickly.

127
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,240
I am deeply grateful.

128
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,840
Time and again,

129
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,200
you've shown us

130
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,480
such generosity.

131
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,520
I'm forever in your debt!

132
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:55,880
Think nothing of it.

133
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,720
As for those...

134
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,680
rather peculiar gifts...

135
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,480
Please, no more of those.

136
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:09,880
Well......

137
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,120
And this...

138
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,720
is also for me?

139
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,000
I...

140
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,880
It's...

141
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,640
You brought it,

142
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:25,800
so leave it.

143
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,480
What is it this time?

144
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:14,760
The last time...

145
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,240
when you came

146
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,320
to my aid...

147
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,240
you left it behind.

148
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,120
I brought it home

149
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,520
and found a few tears in it,

150
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,240
so I had it repaired

151
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,160
with golden thread...

152
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,200
But it still

153
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,760
didn't look right...

154
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,560
so I had it reembroidered...

155
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,040
Remarkable.

156
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,720
Then I shall

157
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,520
gladly keep it.

158
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,040
Yes, my lord.

159
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,400
What's taking Mr. Ping so long?

160
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,679
Stop!

161
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,520
Mr. Ping!

162
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,400
Qingpu,

163
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,440
they've taken

164
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,600
Master Gu!

165
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:42,000
At first,

166
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:44,440
he only wanted a few customers.

167
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,000
Earn a little extra on the sly.

168
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,880
But then he heard,

169
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,760
if you lease the place

170
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,120
and turn it over,

171
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,120
you could take an extra cut.

172
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,840
Then he thought... why not.

173
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,120
Why not?

174
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,560
You useless fool!

175
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,960
My son, MY SON!

176
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,320
Was touting

177
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,600
for a gambling den!

178
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,200
What is this?

179
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,720
That is greed rotting a man

180
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:14,280
from the inside!

181
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,160
Father,

182
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,920
I've already sent Mr. Ping

183
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:18,320
and the men after them.

184
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,600
Shall we

185
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,840
go to the authorities?

186
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,360
Absolutely not...

187
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,800
not the authorities!

188
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:25,720
Jinrong was taken

189
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:28,360
from a gambling den.

190
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,320
What a disgrace!

191
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,440
Report it,

192
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,560
and we proclaim to all

193
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,520
that my son consorted with gamblers.

194
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,680
No, no.

195
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,800
Absolutely not!

196
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,840
My lord!

197
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,640
My lord,

198
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,600
something terrible...

199
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:43,480
My lady heard that

200
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,520
Master Gu has been taken...

201
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:45,400
she has fainted!

202
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,160
What?

203
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,720
I told everyone

204
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,080
she was not to know a word of it!

205
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,440
I swear I didn't say a word...

206
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:05,240
This way.

207
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,880
How did Mother find out

208
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,200
that Jinrong was taken?

209
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,400
I was walking with her in the garden

210
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,680
when two servants

211
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,600
started gossiping,

212
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,440
saying Master Gu

213
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,720
had been seized.

214
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,560
She asked them what happened,

215
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,240
and then she collapsed.

216
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,840
Jinzhao,

217
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,440
how is she?

218
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,200
She's taken the remedies.

219
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,120
She is resting now.

220
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,280
Thank heaven for that.

221
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,880
But Jinrong...

222
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:49,760
I heard

223
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,000
he was abducted!

224
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:53,440
And who

225
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,200
told you that?

226
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,920
Everyone's talking about it!

227
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,640
Jinrong was taken. Yes.

228
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,280
And this was supposed to stay quiet,

229
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,720
especially from Mother.

230
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,120
Someone

231
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,400
let it slip.

232
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,600
Who is it?

233
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,960
Hard to say.

234
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,440
But I'd start by asking

235
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,240
who has the most to gain.

236
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,920
Is Chunlin even trustworthy?

237
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:30,920
What if he slips up!

238
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,120
Have no fear.

239
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,760
We are close.

240
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,080
He won't betray me.

241
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:36,320
Besides,

242
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,200
Jinrong was snatched

243
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:38,800
in broad daylight.

244
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:39,920
Half the city saw it.

245
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,040
Nobody will trace it back to us.

246
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,520
Good.

247
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,360
And Jinrong, honestly,

248
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,680
his mother's fortune

249
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,680
is practically a goldmine.

250
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,760
That's not enough for him?

251
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,840
He had to tout for a gambling den,

252
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,280
trading in that sort of filth.

253
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,440
No wonder his mother fainted.

254
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,160
I'd faint just hearing about it.

255
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,240
Lan...

256
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,560
Tell me the truth.

257
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,560
Was it you who

258
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,360
spread word of this

259
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,720
until she collapsed in despair?

260
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,080
Outrageous!

261
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,680
Guard your tongue...

262
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:08,480
That's right.

263
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,640
We only just found out ourselves.

264
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,520
My lady,

265
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,920
you grieve your mother unjustly!

266
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,040
Then good.

267
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:17,120
Jinrong's fate hangs by a thread.

268
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:17,840
Mind yourselves,

269
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,000
do not fan these flames!

270
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,200
Am I the one

271
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,560
on trial?

272
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:22,960
I gave you life.

273
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,600
Is this how you repay me?

274
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,640
If rage consumes you,

275
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,640
do not bring it

276
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:27,680
to my door!

277
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,000
Lord Chen

278
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,080
has learned of your plight.

279
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,120
Should aid be needed,

280
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,240
present this

281
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,320
to the capital garrison

282
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,240
and seek out Lord Hu.

283
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,160
Boss,

284
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,120
how big's our cut this time?

285
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:08,280
Easy, easy.

286
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,520
You'll all get yours.

287
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:26,080
Sir!

288
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:27,800
Where is he?

289
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:29,040
Woodshed.

290
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,080
Go.

291
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:33,920
Li Xianhuai...

292
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:58,600
Mother...

293
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,040
Is Jinrong back yet?

294
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,480
Don't worry.

295
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,120
Everyone is out looking.

296
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,080
Mr. Luo

297
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,280
has a whole search party out.

298
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:10,880
And Lord Chen

299
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,080
is on it too.

300
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:14,640
Alright.

301
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,240
My lady...

302
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,400
I'll be back.

303
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,880
It was really Li Xianhuai?

304
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,040
Yes.

305
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,640
I would've run back last night,

306
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:36,400
but the city gates

307
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,840
were already closed.

308
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,040
Li Xianhuai is

309
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:41,360
Master Ye's guard.

310
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,560
So does that mean...

311
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:44,240
Master Ye's the one behind it?

312
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:46,720
My lady!

313
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:47,960
My lady!

314
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,200
What is it?

315
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,200
Word just

316
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,120
came from

317
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,000
Master Ye.

318
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,120
