319
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,360
He's sending him back now!

320
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,200
Oh, Mother...

321
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:02,440
I was so terrified...

322
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,280
Mother,

323
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:08,200
Mr. Li is the reason

324
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,000
I'm alive.

325
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:12,040
I cannot thank you enough.

326
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,720
Please, come in

327
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:16,120
