328
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:16,880
Gratitude.

329
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,520
But I must return

330
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,560
to Master Ye.

331
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:19,560
I shouldn't linger.

332
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:21,000
Another time,

333
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:22,000
we'll

334
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,360
