335
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,280
Here, my son.

336
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:41,240
Enough!

337
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,400
Father...

338
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:46,000
He was held by those men

339
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,080
through the night...

340
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,520
He's been through enough.

341
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:50,160
The lesson is learned.

342
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,160
Is that not sufficient?

343
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:55,040
The lesson is learned.

344
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:56,480
Such simple wisdom!

345
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:58,080
Do you know

346
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,320
