347
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:01,840
The censor has denounced me!

348
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:04,400
How did the censor learn of it?

349
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,880
It's an unlicensed gambling den,

350
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,240
