353
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,280
Ledgers showed it

354
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:18,040
clear as day:

355
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:20,080
Gu Jinrong's name.

356
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:23,920
The keeper confessed all:

357
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:27,480
the boy's father

358
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:30,440
heads the Treasury,

359
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,160
so he got special terms:

360
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:34,360
a private room, discounted.

361
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,760
He's lying!

362
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:39,280
Your name. In ink.

363
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:40,600
With your handprint.

364
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,760
And you call him a liar?

365
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:45,520
Were it not for Lord Chen,

366
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:48,000
who vouched for you,

367
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:48,880
you'd already

368
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:52,480
be standing before a judge!

369
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:54,280
Rather than

370
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,160
let you

371
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,760
bring this house to ruin,

372
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,400
today

373
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,400
I will

374
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:04,440
beat you

375
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:06,040
into the ground!

376
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:07,920
Mother!

377
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,680
- Mother!
- Father...

378
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:13,839
My lord!

379
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:14,240
Please!

380
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:15,280
My lord...

381
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:16,560
Father!

382
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:17,599
Stop...

383
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:18,280
My lord,

384
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:19,560
