386
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:22,160
It will kill him!

387
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,240
Out of my way!

388
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,000
My lady...

389
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:26,640
