- Mother...

390
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:29,000
And you...

391
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:30,840
I was just getting to you.

392
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,080
This family has a legacy!

393
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:35,560
