400
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,440
Isn't it!

401
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:54,400
You Jis...

402
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:56,360
raised on money,

403
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:59,240
