406
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,160
Father, do you hear yourself?

407
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,120
Your return to office,

408
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:12,440
paid for by the Jis, every last coin.

409
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:13,960
Currently,

410
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:16,000
house's contents: food, garb, all...

411
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:16,920
which escapes

412
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,400
Mother's funds?

413
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:21,120
You despise us that much?

414
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,400
Then starting today,

415
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:24,640
