416
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,080
All of it.

417
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:26,960
We shall see

418
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:28,160
how far that

419
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:29,480
actually gets you.

420
00:18:30,120 --> 00:18:30,960
- Jinzhao...
- Oh,

421
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:32,440
and your account

422
00:18:32,560 --> 00:18:33,080
