423
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:34,560
Art, antiques.

424
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,000
Settle every last bit.

425
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:37,440
How dare...

426
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:39,400
