427
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,480
You see this?

428
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,760
Your children!

429
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:44,880
Both of them,

430
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,800
son and daughter...

431
00:18:47,040 --> 00:18:48,240
greed is all they know,

432
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,440
