434
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,560
You're crying?

435
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:58,320
I should be the one in tears!

436
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:02,760
I attained the pinnacle

437
00:19:03,080 --> 00:19:04,920
