439
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,040
My fault...

440
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,240
All mine...

441
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:15,880
It's on me...

442
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,120
My Lady!

443
00:19:19,360 --> 00:19:19,960
Mother...

444
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,760
My Lady!

445
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:25,520
My Lady!

446
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:26,240
Are you all right?

447
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:28,240
- Mother...
- My lady!

448
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,200
Mother!

449
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,440
My lady!

450
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:31,960
Ms. Jinzhao's here.

451
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,080
My lady,

452
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:40,880
