453
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:43,560
She woke in the night

454
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:45,720
and hasn't slept since.

455
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,640
Just sitting there.

456
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,280
Staring out.

457
00:20:49,360 --> 00:20:50,560
I am

458
00:20:50,560 --> 00:20:51,600
at a loss.

459
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:53,760
Did my lord come?

460
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:55,200
Just left.

461
00:20:55,840 --> 00:20:57,360
He apologized.

462
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:58,520
But she

463
00:20:58,520 --> 00:20:59,880
didn't say a word

464
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:01,960
in return.

465
00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:04,360
He lost patience

466
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:06,600
