467
00:21:08,520 --> 00:21:09,280
I see.

468
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,640
Mother...

469
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:23,960
Darling,

470
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,160
come,

471
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:26,320
