472
00:21:34,520 --> 00:21:36,400
What beautiful hands.

473
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:41,440
When we sent you to Tongzhou,

474
00:21:43,080 --> 00:21:44,080
they were

475
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:45,920
this big.

476
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:48,920
It was

477
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:51,400
