478
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:55,080
How I wish I could go back...

479
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,600
My lord says it's time.

480
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,320
I'm to take the child.

481
00:22:08,520 --> 00:22:09,320
My lady...

482
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,160
Where is she?

483
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:12,520
Get her out now!

484
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:27,800
My love,

485
00:22:28,320 --> 00:22:29,360
give me the child.

486
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,880
My lord.

487
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,760
She's barely

488
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:35,160
one month old.

489
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:39,000
After all I endured

490
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,240
