504
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,960
Enough of this.

505
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,400
Hand her over!

506
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,040
My lord...

507
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:18,040
