- Give her here!

508
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:18,840
My lord...

509
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:22,360
please...

510
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:23,520
My lord...

511
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:25,200
Hear me out!

512
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,920
Wait, please!

513
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:34,320
My child!

514
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,000
No, no!

515
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:36,600
My lady...

516
00:23:36,760 --> 00:23:37,480
- No!
- My lady...

517
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,440
My lord!

518
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:39,400
- My lady...
- Please...

519
00:23:39,840 --> 00:23:41,920
You've barely left childbed.

520
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:43,800
My baby!

521
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:46,080
Jinzhao!

522
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:50,080
Jinzhao!

523
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:58,080
