527
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:18,000
Jinzhao...

528
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:19,640
Forgive me...

529
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,240
Forgive me.

530
00:24:22,320 --> 00:24:24,160
I failed you, my child.

531
00:24:25,800 --> 00:24:27,280
If I've wronged

532
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,640
