536
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:40,080
The greatest sin of my life

537
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:42,920
was committed

538
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,040
against you.

539
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:48,960
I'll carry this guilt

540
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:52,160
to my grave...

541
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:08,480
Mother...

542
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:51,520
[The greatest sin of my life]

543
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:54,240
[was committed]

544
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,400
[against you.]

545
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:18,160
[Mother...]

546
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,000
My lady,

547
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:37,280
