548
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:38,600
It's nothing.

549
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,920
Dust in my eyes.

550
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:47,440
Go to Lord Changxing's.

551
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:48,800
Find Li Xianhuai.

552
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,560
Tell him

553
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:56,320
I wish to thank Master Ye

554
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:58,240
for bringing Jinrong home.

555
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:03,160
I shall treat him to wine.

556
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,680
Those were her words?

557
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:10,400
Yes, my lord.

558
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,040
she requests the pleasure

559
00:28:12,040 --> 00:28:12,960
of your company,

560
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,120
at your leisure.

561
00:28:17,360 --> 00:28:18,440
At last.

562
00:28:19,320 --> 00:28:21,000
Worth every bit of trouble.

563
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:24,880
Greetings, Master Ye.

564
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:27,560
My gratitude for saving my brother.

565
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:28,280
Such etiquette.

566
00:28:28,280 --> 00:28:29,320
I'm not sure

567
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,720
I know this lady.

568
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:34,000
Your kindness demands a worthy return.

569
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,640
You've done my family

570
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,640
