571
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,480
You deserve proper gratitude.

572
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:53,440
Awfully quiet in here.

573
00:28:54,520 --> 00:28:55,960
Few customers at this hour.

574
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,040
Which suite

575
00:28:58,360 --> 00:28:59,520
have you arranged?

576
00:29:00,320 --> 00:29:01,520
Our finest.

577
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,640
We do not

578
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:03,640
open it

579
00:29:04,080 --> 00:29:05,000
for just anyone.

580
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,280
But today,

581
00:29:06,520 --> 00:29:07,680
you are not

582
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,000
just anyone.

583
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:12,960
Lead the way.

584
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:14,080
Mr. Li,

585
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,560
My lady has prepared

586
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:17,640
