588
00:29:20,320 --> 00:29:20,960
I...

589
00:29:22,360 --> 00:29:22,800
Enjoy yourselves.

590
00:29:23,080 --> 00:29:23,600
Yes, my lord.

591
00:29:23,840 --> 00:29:24,400
Gentlemen.

592
00:29:26,760 --> 00:29:27,480
After you.

593
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:39,440
What manner of game

594
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,520
