595
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:42,040
Tell me,

596
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,200
you took Jinrong.

597
00:29:44,840 --> 00:29:46,000
Then you let him go.

598
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:48,000
What were you after?

599
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,680
You found out.

600
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,120
How?

601
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:53,760
Someone told you?

602
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:56,960
Don't tell me

603
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:58,920
it was Chen Yanyun...

604
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,040
You two keep

605
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,280
