606
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:03,560
So

607
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:04,840
that's a yes.

608
00:30:06,320 --> 00:30:07,240
Every bit of it.

609
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:08,680
Yes,

610
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:09,840
I did it.

611
00:30:10,280 --> 00:30:10,960
Why?

612
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:12,680
He never did

613
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,680
a single thing to you!

614
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:15,040
Why would you go after him?

615
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:16,920
No reason.

616
00:30:17,840 --> 00:30:18,520
It diverted me.

617
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:27,960
Oh, there it is.

618
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:29,800
The real you!

619
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:35,200
You left me no choice.

620
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:37,200
Master Ye,

621
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,680
I cannot fathom

622
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,360
why you took him.

623
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:43,760
Nor can I fathom you,

624
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:44,960
not even after all this time.

625
00:30:46,320 --> 00:30:47,280
Every time I begin to think

626
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:47,800
perhaps there is

627
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:48,960
something decent in you,

628
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,360
you do something

629
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,880
that defies all reason.

630
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,120
So forgive me

631
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:54,960
for meeting madness with madness.

632
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:56,280
Lest one day

633
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,200
you burn my house down

634
00:30:58,560 --> 00:30:59,560
simply because the mood struck you.

635
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:00,920
Is that genuine confusion,

636
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,080
or are you putting it on?

637
00:31:02,560 --> 00:31:03,240
Pardon?

638
00:31:03,560 --> 00:31:04,560
Everything I did.

639
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:06,080
I did it for you.

640
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:07,920
What do you mean?

641
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,440
The boy is barely grown

642
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:13,040
and he's already touting for gambling dens.

643
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:15,080
A scolding changes nothing.

644
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:16,520
If you actually

645
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,280
want him to stop,

646
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:20,400
you shake him.

647
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:21,920
Hard enough

648
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,520
that it sticks.

649
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,520
That's the only way.

650
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:27,000
That was

651
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:28,360
your reasoning?

652
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:31,120
What business is it of yours?

653
00:31:31,120 --> 00:31:32,040
Because!

654
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:36,120
Because...

655
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:37,520
you are fearless in every matter

656
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:39,040
except when

657
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:40,280
it concerns your own blood.

658
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:43,120
You saved my life once.

659
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:45,600
I had no worthy means of repayment.

660
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,880
So let me handle the part

661
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:49,240
you couldn't

662
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,440
bring yourself to do.

663
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,400
And I was measured about it.

664
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:54,720
After what he endured,

665
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:55,840
he will not

666
00:31:55,840 --> 00:31:57,000
go near a gambling den again.

667
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,560
Do you even realize

668
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:02,360
because of what you did,

669
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:03,800
my mother

670
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,120
collapsed.

671
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,480
Her health

672
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,680
was already fragile.

673
00:32:11,520 --> 00:32:12,320
And then Jinrong...

674
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:13,160
this whole thing...

675
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,520
pushed her over the edge.

676
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,960
She hasn't

677
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:17,760
left her bed since yesterday.

678
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:21,920
I...

679
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,040
I had no idea.

680
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:27,000
I was only trying to help...

681
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,080
Well, thank you for that!

682
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:29,440
Don't help me again.

683
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:33,600
How dare you, woman!

684
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:34,640
Untie me this instant!

685
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,480
Your brother's the one

686
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:37,960
who put your mother in bed!

687
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:41,000
I only meant to help.

688
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:46,240
There it is.

689
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:47,880
I struck a nerve.

690
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:49,800
Snap at me?

691
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:51,120
Go fix your brother first.

692
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:54,360
So I'm the only one

693
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,520
you dare lash out at!

694
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:00,400
Stay down.

695
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,440
You've earned it!

696
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:04,320
Gu Jinzhao!

697
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:05,640
Hey!

698
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:51,680
Master,

699
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:53,840
I looked into it.

700
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:55,360
The gambling den

701
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:56,280
wasn't raided

702
00:33:56,280 --> 00:33:57,000
over paperwork.

703
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,400
It was raided on suspicion

704
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,920
of harboring some outlaws.

705
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:01,400
The garrison

706
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:02,840
carried out the operation,

707
00:34:03,360 --> 00:34:04,080
but the order

708
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,640
came from the bureau.

709
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,720
And the garrison

710
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:08,840
sent men

711
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,679
specifically for Master Gu.

712
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,639
It seems Lord Chen was the one

713
00:34:12,639 --> 00:34:13,400
who arranged for that.

714
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,719
The whole trip

715
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:57,640
paid off.

716
00:34:58,040 --> 00:34:58,800
I came upon

717
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:00,080
a herb farmer,

718
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:02,160
a man who knew

719
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:03,320
Mr. Xiao well.

720
00:35:04,600 --> 00:35:06,120
He spoke of his gift

721
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,400
for medicine

722
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,600
with

723
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,800
great admiration.

724
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:10,920
People practically

725
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:11,720
revered him for it.

726
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:14,080
One night,

727
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:15,080
after too much wine,

728
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,480
he let slip that

729
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:18,320
he was from Xianghe.

730
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:20,040
And behind his house

731
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,200
stood a temple.

732
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:22,680
As a boy,

733
00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:24,440
he used to slip inside and steal offerings.

734
00:35:25,080 --> 00:35:26,600
A temple in Xianghe.

735
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,080
Could it be Xuanmiao Temple?

736
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:32,920
My thoughts precisely.

737
00:35:33,720 --> 00:35:35,440
The temple holds royal patronage.

738
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,200
Royals have long dedicated

739
00:35:37,200 --> 00:35:38,600
their children there since birth.

740
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,120
Prince Chengqing was no exception.

741
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,000
And his appearance?

742
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,120
Was anything said of that?

743
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:45,480
The sort of face one forgets.

744
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,200
One thing only,

745
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:48,960
a small growth on his left ear.

746
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:51,120
My lord.

747
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,120
A letter from Lord Zhang.

748
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:13,120
Zhang Ling has broken them.

749
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:14,720
Over 200

750
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:15,920
of them in total.

751
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:16,960
Divided into five cells.

752
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:18,680
Each one in the dark about the others.

753
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:20,160
A single courier

754
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,520
moves between them.

755
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:22,680
Passes instructions.

756
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:23,960
Nobody knows

757
00:36:24,160 --> 00:36:24,680
where this

758
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:26,000
courier lives.

759
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:28,760
Only one detail

760
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,480
slipped out:

761
00:36:32,120 --> 00:36:33,080
he consumes no meat.

762
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,440
A strict vegan.

763
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:39,120
Send word

764
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:41,480
to Lord Zhang.

765
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:42,560
Look into the temple.

766
00:36:43,120 --> 00:36:43,720
My lord.

767
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:34,120
Darling...

768
00:37:34,120 --> 00:37:35,440
no more healers.

769
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,760
It serves nothing.

770
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:42,160
They all write

771
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:44,680
the same prescriptions.

772
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,400
Sit up, lie down,

773
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,160
sit up again.

774
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:54,000
If Death has marked my name,

775
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:56,400
no remedies will spare me.

776
00:37:58,240 --> 00:37:59,000
Mother,

777
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:00,600
please.

778
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:02,400
The healer said

779
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,200
it is not so grave.

780
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:06,760
You simply need time.

781
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:09,000
Let yourself heal.

782
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,040
What is it?

783
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:19,920
I was just assigned

784
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:21,280
to look after the young master.

785
00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:22,320
This was... found

786
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:23,600
beneath his pillow.

787
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,680
[It is I who brought this upon Mother.]

788
00:38:41,200 --> 00:38:42,280
[Upon all of you.]

789
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,960
[From this day forward,]

790
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,600
[forget that I ever existed.]

791
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,400
That miserable,

792
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:49,520
ungrateful boy!

793
00:38:51,240 --> 00:38:52,480
Has he...

794
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:54,000
run away?

795
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:55,480
Father,

796
00:38:55,640 --> 00:38:56,840
we shall find him!

797
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:57,880
For what?

798
00:38:58,720 --> 00:38:59,680
He will keep

799
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,840
making trouble until

800
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:04,520
this family is ruined!

801
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:05,640
Let him go!

802
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:06,560
Good riddance

803
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:08,040
to him!

804
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:09,960
Father,

805
00:39:10,240 --> 00:39:11,080
this is not the moment

806
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,760
for words you'll regret!

807
00:39:14,040 --> 00:39:14,760
Qingpu,

808
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:16,200
find Mr. Ping.

809
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,960
Take everyone we have.

810
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,400
Whoever finds him

811
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:20,360
will be handsomely rewarded.

812
00:39:20,720 --> 00:39:21,920
My lady!

813
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:26,880
Chunlin,

814
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,920
send our men as well.

815
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:29,520
At once.

816
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,320
[The temple holds royal patronage.]

817
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,000
[Without an imperial edict,]

818
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:42,920
[the bureau]

819
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:44,400
[has no grounds to conduct a search.]

820
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,120
[We will need a pretext.]

821
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:53,280
His Highness' charm has been

822
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,560
ready for a while.

823
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,080
We were planning to send it

824
00:39:57,080 --> 00:39:58,400
at the start of next month.

825
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:01,640
We did not expect to see you.

826
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:04,000
It's the Crown Prince's charm.

827
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,200
Coming in person

828
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:06,400
was the right thing to do.

829
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,840
These beads

830
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:13,720
are a small gift.

831
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:16,920
Nothing of great worth,

832
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,440
but they've been

833
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:21,200
blessed by the gods.

834
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:22,760
Gratitude.

835
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:26,440
Lord Zhang!

836
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:29,440
Something tells me

837
00:40:29,640 --> 00:40:31,640
you are looking for someone.

838
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:43,040
You see right through me.

839
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:44,520
I'll be plain about it.

840
00:40:45,200 --> 00:40:46,680
Has anyone of a suspicious nature

841
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:48,680
been seen recently?

842
00:40:49,560 --> 00:40:50,880
What sort of person?

843
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:53,200
Someone suspected of... sedition.

844
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,280
No.

845
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,360
We have

846
00:40:58,360 --> 00:41:00,120
47 members of staff in total.

847
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:03,440
All have been registered

848
00:41:03,560 --> 00:41:05,000
with the authorities.

849
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,800
And beyond those people?

850
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:08,960
Casual laborers,

851
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:10,160
kitchen hands?

852
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:11,800
None whatsoever.

853
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:15,480
Given the royals' connection to us,

854
00:41:15,680 --> 00:41:17,400
we cannot afford to be careless.

855
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:20,440
They are all trustworthy.

856
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:22,880
Even the farmers who deliver our vegetables

857
00:41:23,080 --> 00:41:25,040
are from households down the hill.

858
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:27,320
Unless...

859
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:29,560
My child,

860
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:33,160
have there been any outsiders lately?

861
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:36,680
Yes, Master.

862
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:38,720
There has been a devotee.

863
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,000
What does he look like?

864
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:41,920
Thin. Dark complexion.

865
00:41:42,640 --> 00:41:43,240
Oh,

866
00:41:43,480 --> 00:41:44,680
there's a growth

867
00:41:44,680 --> 00:41:45,720
on his left ear.

868
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:47,200
He told me

869
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:49,080
he calls it his doorstop.

870
00:41:50,480 --> 00:41:51,600
Where is he now?

871
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:53,000
He just left.

872
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,640
Right when you were arriving.

873
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,960
He cannot have gone far.

874
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,160
Ride hard,

875
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:10,440
we may still catch him!

876
00:42:14,680 --> 00:42:15,400
Ambush!

877
00:42:23,840 --> 00:42:24,720
Cover your faces!

878
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,520
My lord!

879
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:05,000
What's happened?

880
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:06,080
My lady,

881
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:07,640
a wheel gave out.

882
00:43:08,160 --> 00:43:09,240
We won't be moving

883
00:43:09,240 --> 00:43:10,040
any time soon.

884
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:11,720
There's

885
00:43:12,080 --> 00:43:13,400
an abandoned shed just ahead.

886
00:43:13,600 --> 00:43:14,600
Let's take shelter there.

887
00:43:24,120 --> 00:43:25,280
The rain is letting up.

888
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:30,880
Listen carefully,

889
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:32,880
whoever finds Jinrong

890
00:43:33,280 --> 00:43:35,000
gets 100 taels of silver.

891
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:36,480
Yes, my lady!

892
00:43:44,640 --> 00:43:45,240
My lord,

893
00:43:45,760 --> 00:43:46,840
we're almost there.

894
00:43:56,720 --> 00:43:57,640
Lord Chen?

895
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:02,560
My lord,

896
00:44:02,960 --> 00:44:03,720
brace yourself.

897
00:44:14,560 --> 00:44:15,160
My lady,

898
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:16,760
should I lend a hand?

899
00:44:17,920 --> 00:44:18,880
I'll go.

900
00:44:21,480 --> 00:44:22,120
Let me.

901
00:44:31,280 --> 00:44:32,240
I'm grateful, my lady.

902
00:44:52,600 --> 00:44:54,000
[How did he end up like this...]
